WEBVTT

00:15.173 --> 00:16.292
Why am I a snowboarder?

00:17.535 --> 00:18.408
Total freedom.

00:20.927 --> 00:25.247
When I'm on a mountain, I choose where, when and how I ride.

00:36.657 --> 00:38.703
Whether my friends and I are just messing around...

00:41.639 --> 00:46.718
...or finding secret spots, out here it's all about fun.

00:50.769 --> 00:53.520
So when you're ready to conquer the extreme peak conditions,...

00:54.950 --> 01:06.800
...explore the back country or compete at the terrain parks, get on board.

01:46.395 --> 01:48.345
Out of the way!

01:54.688 --> 01:55.976
Shaun White Snowboarding.

01:56.075 --> 01:57.267
In stores, November 16.

01:57.345 --> 01:58.257
Rated E10 to Teen.

